            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is softening, trim your<strong> green beans</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and slice your<strong> carrot[s]</strong> into thin discs</p><p>Add the<strong> trimmed green beans</strong> and<strong> carrot</strong> <strong>discs</strong> to a large piece of <strong>tin foil</strong> with 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span>[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong>, a small knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Scrunch the foil around the vegetables to form a tightly sealed parcel (or two!) and add it to a baking tray, then set aside for later – this is your <strong>vegetable parcel</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1681316490694-x200.jpg",
