    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> coronation chicken pie </strong>topped with a <strong>pie lid</strong> and the <strong>buttery veg</strong> to the side</p><p>Season with <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
